OL,3,CTwo-thirds of young people think
OL,4,Cvaping is 'socially acceptable'
OL,6,FMore than nine in ten of those
OL,7,Fsurveyed across Jersey and Guernsey
OL,8,Falso felt that more should be done to
OL,9,Fsupport schools with the introduction
OL,10,Fof measures that would prevent people
OL,11,Ffrom vaping in educational settings.
OL,13,FThe research comes as both islands
OL,14,Frecently introduced measures to try
OL,15,Fand curb the rise of vaping, such as
OL,16,Fbanning disposable vapes and taxing
OL,17,Fvape liquid.
